<h1>Blog</h1>
<p>Field notes on shipping software — backend, DevOps, data, and AI automation. Written by Robin Ward.</p>

<ul class="post-list">
{% for post in collections.posts %}
    <li>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <div class="date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
        {% if post.data.description %}<p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
    </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
